o River]]\n |\n | [[Union Pacific Railroad|UP]] [[Utah Division (D&RGW)|Green River Subdivision]] (ex-[[Denver and Rio Grande Western Railroad|D&RGW]])\n|-\n | [[Salina Canyon]]\n | Sevier\n | [[Salina Creek]]\n | {{sort|070|[[Interstate 70 in Utah|I-70]]}}\n | [[Old Spanish Trail (trade route)|Old Spanish Trail]]\n|-\n | [[Salt Creek Canyon]]\n | Juab\n | [[Salt Creek (Utah)|Salt Creek]]\n | {{sort|132|[[Utah State Route 132|SR-132]]}}<!--and Nebo Loop Road? topos don't label this canyon-->\n |\n|-\n | [[Sevenmile Canyon]]\n | San Juan\n |\n | {{sort|313|[[Utah State Route 313|SR-313]]}}\n |\n|-\n | [[Snow Canyon]]\n | Washington\n |\n |\n |\n|-\n | [[Soldier Canyon (Carbon County, Utah)|Soldier Canyon]]<br>(Carbon County)\n | Carbon\n | [[Soldier Creek (Utah)|Soldier Creek]]\n | [[Nine Mile Canyon Road]]\n |\n|-\n | [[Soldier Canyon (Sevier County, Utah)|Soldier Canyon]]<br>(Sevier County)\n | Sevier\n |\n |\n | [[Old Spanish Trail (trade route)|Old Spanish Trail]]\n|-\n | [[South Fork Canyon]]\n | Weber\n | [[South Fork Ogden River]]\n | {{sort|039|[[Utah State Route 39|SR-39]]}}\n |\n|-\n | [[Spanish Fork Canyon]]\n | Utah\n | [[Spanish Fork River]], [[Soldier Creek (Utah)|Soldier Creek]]\n | {{sort|006|[[U.S. Route 6 in Utah|US-6]]}}\n | [[Union Pacific Railroad|UP]] [[Utah Division (D&RGW)|Provo Subdivision]] (ex-[[Denver and Rio Grande Western Railroad|D&RGW]])\n|-\n | [[Split Mountain Canyon]]\n | Uintah\n | [[Green River (Colorado River tributary)|Green River]]\n |\n |\n|-\n | [[Stillwater Canyon]]\n | San Juan, Wayne\n | [[Green River (Colorado River tributary)|Green River]]\n |\n |\n|-\n | [[Swallow Canyon]]\n | Daggett\n | [[Green River (Colorado River tributary)|Green River]]\n |\n |\n|-\n | [[Weber Canyon]]\n | Davis, Morgan, Weber\n | [[Weber River]]\n | {{sort|084|[[Interstate 84 in Utah|I-84]]}}\n |\n|-\n | [[Wellsville Canyon]]\n | Cache\n |\n | {{sort|089|[[U.S. Route 89 in Utah|US-89]]}}, [[U.S. Route 91|US-91]]\n |\n|-\n | [[Westwater Canyon]]\n